# CODEOWNERS
# Defines which individuals or teams that are responsible for the contents of a repository.

# Automatically set the code owners as mandatory reviewers by: 
# 1. Going to the branch protection rules in the repository settings
# 2. Edit the settings for an existing rule or create a new rule
# 3. Check the box "Require review from Code Owners"  under "Require a pull request before merging" and save the rule
# When a PR is marked as Ready for Review, the code owners will be automatically tagged as reviewers

# See the GitHub Docs for more information, including syntax and examples.
# Link: https://docs.github.com/en/repositories/managing-your-repositorys-settings-and-features/customizing-your-repository/about-code-owners

